  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Group Consolidation Specialist",
  "description": "<p>A leading multinational scientific instruments and solutions company is seeking a Group Consolidation Specialist to join its Singapore office for an expansion hire. The successful candidate will play a key role in managing financial consolidation and reporting, and to drive process improvement.</p><p>Reporting to the Consolidation Manager, the incumbent will work in a team of 5 staffs. He / She will need to hands-on group consolidation and be involved in OneStream implementation project, responsible for system integration and process enhancement.</p><p>Successful applicants will work in a collaborative environment with exposure to multinational accounting, cross-border processes, and opportunities for professional growth.</p><p><strong>REQUIREMENTS</strong></p><ul><li>Bachelor’s degree in Accounting, Finance, or a related discipline.</li><li>Post-grad qualifications such as CA, CPA, and Masters would be advantageous</li><li>Min 7 years of accounting work experience, with strong knowledge in IFRS, and consolidation practices.</li><li>Prior work experience in big 4 audit firm is preferred</li><li>Proven track record in group consolidation within multinational corporations</li><li>Hands-on experience with SAP or OneStream is a plus</li><li>Involvement in accounting system implementations and process improvements will be preferred</li></ul><p>Interested applicants kindly use the apply button or send in your application in MS word format to Anson.lim@onyxrecruit.com.sg. (EA: 18C9213 / R21103164)</p><p>*We regret that due to potential volume of responses, not all candidates will be contacted.</p>",
